{"tid":344190,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"9月去和歌山有咩好做","createTime":"2017-08-02T05:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T08:21:50.000Z","uid":103498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a95e63c06e1e3c3f4aa18e2143a08857ad9e054","tid":344190,"uid":103498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"9月頭同屋企人去大阪加和歌山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n和歌山可以有咩搞作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b3ba491ed2e980ea6613c327d17d2de9c9f537","tid":344190,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"除左浸溫泉係冇野做<br />\n啲鋪好早關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2474f79a2dd04ef52db5a47a0d3f6e3b8991ea64","tid":344190,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"鍾意影景既話好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c0810227cfbe4daee1862c45bdab65ba204394","tid":344190,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"白浜 <br />\n1.自己買定啲煙花響海邊玩啦~<br />\n2.景<br />\n3.溫泉<br />\n4.とれとれ市場<br />\n<br />\n那智<br />\n1.瀑布<br />\n2.大社<br />\n3.島上果間酒店<br />\n<br />\n和歌山市<br />\n1. 黑潮市場<br />\n2. 和歌山城<br />\n3. 遠啲就貓車站<br />\n<br />\n其他就自己搵啦..."},{"pid":"71cca10390f90d6590600d1afc67a40584c12362","tid":344190,"uid":73231,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"大阪搭くろしお去和歌山其實幾快<br />\n關西PASS 包自由席... 不過好似要呢張先去到新宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hiroshima%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5e710838\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/</a><br />\n但呢張可以去埋姬路/神戶/廣島<br />\n但其實五日唔夠去哂咁多地方<br />\n但包咗 HARUKA 同和歌山電鐡都OK<br />\n<br />\n貴少少有七日PASS<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hokuriku/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hokuriku%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=88043e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hokuriku/</a><br />\n不過呢張唔到廣島<br />\n<br />\n兩張都可以去探奧巴馬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近嘅有好多香港人嘅和歌山城,貴志駅,たまⅡ世駅長 , 白浜溫泉<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wakayama-dentetsu.co.jp/sstama/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakayama-dentetsu.co.jp%2Fsstama%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=51949994\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wakayama-dentetsu.co.jp/sstama/</a><br />\n<br />\n白浜溫泉附近有<br />\n三段壁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332743453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanki-shirahama.com%2Fsearch%2Fdetails.php%3Flog%3D1332743453&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e1d3a521\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332743453</a><br />\n<br />\n千畳敷<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332737678&amp;nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanki-shirahama.com%2Fsearch%2Fdetails.php%3Flog%3D1332737678%26nav%3D1&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4a5d1bf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332737678&amp;nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n円月島<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332736052&amp;nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanki-shirahama.com%2Fsearch%2Fdetails.php%3Flog%3D1332736052%26nav%3D1&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e7252671\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332736052&amp;nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有個海鮮市場<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.toretore.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.toretore.info&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=10acf749\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.toretore.info</a><br />\n<br />\n住宿有間民宿有個出名嘅若女将 真人幾靚女<br />\n佢個海の幸晚餐超正... 佢哋有自己船<br />\n唯一唔好係冇自己廁所... 同埋佢哋啲英文好麻麻.. 基本上係日文溝通<br />\n不過單單晚餐就已經值返個價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再遠少少有世界遺產 熊野三山<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/kumanokodo-isegi/sanzan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakayama-kanko.or.jp%2Fworldheritage%2Fkumanokodo-isegi%2Fsanzan.html&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e89252db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/kumanokodo-isegi/sanzan.html</a><br />\n<br />\n熊野古道<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hongu.jp/kumanokodo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongu.jp%2Fkumanokodo%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b509e11e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hongu.jp/kumanokodo/</a><br />\n<br />\n高野山<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/koyasan1200/contents/midokoro.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakayama-kanko.or.jp%2Fworldheritage%2Fkoyasan1200%2Fcontents%2Fmidokoro.html&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a4dd3eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/koyasan1200/contents/midokoro.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附近有<br />\n那智の滝<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nachikan.jp/kumano/nachinotaki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nachikan.jp%2Fkumano%2Fnachinotaki%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3c1bd49b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nachikan.jp/kumano/nachinotaki/</a><br />\n<br />\n勝浦マグロ<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nachikan.jp/oshirase/maguro-map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nachikan.jp%2Foshirase%2Fmaguro-map%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=70e2147e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nachikan.jp/oshirase/maguro-map/</a><br />\n<br />\n勝浦温泉<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nachikan.jp/onsen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nachikan.jp%2Fonsen%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bdf06341\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nachikan.jp/onsen/</a><br />\n<br />\n熊野那智大社<br />\n<a href=\"http://kumanonachitaisha.or.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkumanonachitaisha.or.jp&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=90f8220f\" target=\"_blank\">http://kumanonachitaisha.or.jp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得睇中手信要買... 原本以為返關西機場仲有得買... <br />\n但機場得京阪神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有時間, 可以考慮去埋三重<br />\n鳥羽, 志摩, 伊勢都好值得去"},{"pid":"b87f2f6917a8790c57a0990353c9049d888a3958","tid":344190,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大阪搭くろしお去和歌山其實幾快<br />\n關西PASS 包自由席... 不過好似要呢張先去到新宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hiroshima%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5e710838\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hiroshima/</a><br />\n但呢張可以去埋姬路/神戶/廣島<br />\n但其實五日唔夠去哂咁多地方<br />\n但包咗 HARUKA 同和歌山電鐡都OK<br />\n<br />\n貴少少有七日PASS<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hokuriku/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fticket%2Fpass%2Fkansai_hokuriku%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=88043e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/en/ticket/pass/kansai_hokuriku/</a><b