l4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=51949994\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wakayama-dentetsu.co.jp/sstama/</a><br />\n<br />\n白浜溫泉附近有<br />\n三段壁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332743453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanki-shirahama.com%2Fsearch%2Fdetails.php%3Flog%3D1332743453&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e1d3a521\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332743453</a><br />\n<br />\n千畳敷<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332737678&amp;nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanki-shirahama.com%2Fsearch%2Fdetails.php%3Flog%3D1332737678%26nav%3D1&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4a5d1bf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332737678&amp;nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n円月島<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332736052&amp;nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nanki-shirahama.com%2Fsearch%2Fdetails.php%3Flog%3D1332736052%26nav%3D1&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e7252671\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nanki-shirahama.com/search/details.php?log=1332736052&amp;nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有個海鮮市場<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.toretore.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.toretore.info&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=10acf749\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.toretore.info</a><br />\n<br />\n住宿有間民宿有個出名嘅若女将 真人幾靚女<br />\n佢個海の幸晚餐超正... 佢哋有自己船<br />\n唯一唔好係冇自己廁所... 同埋佢哋啲英文好麻麻.. 基本上係日文溝通<br />\n不過單單晚餐就已經值返個價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再遠少少有世界遺產 熊野三山<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/kumanokodo-isegi/sanzan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakayama-kanko.or.jp%2Fworldheritage%2Fkumanokodo-isegi%2Fsanzan.html&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e89252db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/kumanokodo-isegi/sanzan.html</a><br />\n<br />\n熊野古道<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hongu.jp/kumanokodo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongu.jp%2Fkumanokodo%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b509e11e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hongu.jp/kumanokodo/</a><br />\n<br />\n高野山<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/koyasan1200/contents/midokoro.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakayama-kanko.or.jp%2Fworldheritage%2Fkoyasan1200%2Fcontents%2Fmidokoro.html&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a4dd3eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wakayama-kanko.or.jp/worldheritage/koyasan1200/contents/midokoro.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附近有<br />\n那智の滝<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nachikan.jp/kumano/nachinotaki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nachikan.jp%2Fkumano%2Fnachinotaki%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3c1bd49b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nachikan.jp/kumano/nachinotaki/</a><br />\n<br />\n勝浦マグロ<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nachikan.jp/oshirase/maguro-map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nachikan.jp%2Foshirase%2Fmaguro-map%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=70e2147e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nachikan.jp/oshirase/maguro-map/</a><br />\n<br />\n勝浦温泉<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nachikan.jp/onsen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nachikan.jp%2Fonsen%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bdf06341\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nachikan.jp/onsen/</a><br />\n<br />\n熊野那智大社<br />\n<a href=\"http://kumanonachitaisha.or.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkumanonachitaisha.or.jp&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=90f8220f\" target=\"_blank\">http://kumanonachitaisha.or.jp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得睇中手信要買... 原本以為返關西機場仲有得買... <br />\n但機場得京阪神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有時間, 可以考慮去埋三重<br />\n鳥羽, 志摩, 伊勢都好值得去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 我地自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要我一個人plan哂7日行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自駕就去遠少少，柴田絲打介紹嘅都係好地方"},{"pid":"94e8e3de75a538a7207eb1987bca9cde386f2e1c","tid":344190,"uid":24245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:32:31.000Z","msg":"下星期都係同屋企人去呢到自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留個靚名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22dda309380f96ab1398f81f51a636672b3b876","tid":344190,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期都係同屋企人去呢到自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留個靚名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我聽講落和歌山好多 tunnel 路費唔平<br />\n不過自己冇去過 唔肯定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果去三重可以考慮名古屋還車<br />\n<br />\n伊勢神宮前個橫丁好多嘢睇好多嘢食<br />\n不過早閂<br />\n之後可以行 skyline <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iseshima-kanko.jp/en/see-and-do/1310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iseshima-kanko.jp%2Fen%2Fsee-and-do%2F1310&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6e12e1e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.iseshima-kanko.jp/en/see-and-do/1310</a><br />\n360 view 真係幾靚 不過山路少少多彎<br />\n<br />\n和歌山都有條類似好似但我冇行過 <br />\n應該都靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.visitwakayama.jp/venues/venue_24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.visitwakayama.jp%2Fvenues%2Fvenue_24%2F&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3e08fcfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.visitwakayama.jp/venues/venue_24/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似 &yen;1200 由伊勢神宮去鳥羽嗰邊<br />\n有間民宿超正但唔係好敢些牙好想自私留畀自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n房一般但晚餐超超超正<br />\n<br />\n鳥羽落少少可以去海女小屋 聽海女講經歷同食超新鮮海鮮 可惜伊勢エビ仲係休漁期 不過好多地方有鮑魚食如果你鍾意<br />\n個人麻麻<br />\n不過海女要一早預約 我去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後當然係上松阪食和牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上次趕得滯食唔到但聽講超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後去名古屋還車"},{"pid":"727aeab574450a544134e4155b143353591a024a","tid":344190,"uid":72399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"早兩年去勝浦住2晚 <br />\n中之島 &amp; 浦島<br />\n<br />\n人又少正到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590fa829cce21dfdcc0b4aff4af7a847ecad81b7","tid":344190,"uid":24245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下星期都係同屋企人去呢到自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留個靚名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我聽講落和歌山好多 tunnel 路費唔平<br />\n不過自己冇去過 唔肯定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果去三重可以考慮名古屋還車<br />\n<br />\n伊勢神宮前個橫丁好多嘢睇好多嘢食<br />\n不過早閂<br />\n之後可以行 skyline <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.iseshima-kanko.jp/en/see-and-do/1310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iseshima-kanko.jp%2Fen%2Fsee-and-do%2F1310&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml4y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FE